introduction.p:
Let \uppermatring_2(\R) represent the space of 2 \times 2 upper triangular matrices,
and let

	\amp \funcdef{T}{\poly_2(\R)}{\matrixring_2(\R)} \text{,} \amp
	\amp \funcdef{S}{\uppermatring_2(\R)}{\poly_2(\R)}

be defined by


		T(a x^2 + b x + c) = \begin{bmatrix} a + b \amp b + c \\ 0 \amp c \end{bmatrix}
		\text{,}

		S\left(\begin{bmatrix} a \amp b \\ 0 \amp c \end{bmatrix}\right)
		= (a - b + c) x^2 + (b - c) x + c

.

Consider \funcdef{T}{\poly_2(\R)}{\matrixring_2(\R)}
defined by
 T(a x^2 + b x + c) = \begin{bmatrix} 0 \amp a + b + c \\ 0 \amp 0 \end{bmatrix} .

task.p:
Compute the image vector  T(x^2 - 1) 
(and compare with
).
